history.content:
Hello World,

I have already enrolled in cs186W and two other classes. 

However, now since phase 2 is coming up I wanted to add a few more classes. However, on schedule planner, any other class that I put with databases always results in there being no schedule:

"Computer Science W186 does not have any available options with the settings you have selected."

I am concerned because when my enrollment time comes up I do not want to have some classes on my shopping cart only to know last minute that they do not work. Then I will simply lose my seats in those classes. I am unsure what to do. 

------------------------

This issue occurs if I for example have CS186W and Class B enrolled. I then go and deselect class B from the shopping cart area on schedule planner and select Class B from above (Courses) unlocked. I then get the issue that there is no schedule available when I click generate schedules.

Thanks
